I see the issue! The firmware is outputting `ACT PUMP OFF` right after receiving `SENSE LEVEL 20` when it should be outputting `ACT PUMP ON`. This means my controller implementation has a bug.

Looking at my code:
```c
/* Turn pump ON when LEVEL < 30 */
if (controller->last_level < CONTROLLER_LEVEL_LOW_THRESHOLD) {
    controller->pump_on = true;
    controller->state = CONTROLLER_STATE_PUMPING;
